				<td colspan="2"><span>Muse offers the 15% increase to DoTs as well as direct damage.  Rizlona's is a 15% boost to direct damage only.
<br />

<br />
That's what &quot;Restriction (Spell) - Instant spells only&quot; in the Rizlona's text means.
<br />

<br />
So necros, shaman, and druids love Muse.</span></td>
