				<td colspan="2"><span>They are the same except RCoF has one extra restriction:
<br />
Restriction (Spell) - Instant spells only;
<br />

<br />
So Muse is basically Riz but will also work on dots.  I love grouping with a druid/shaman/necro and having them start muttering in group chat how their dots are acting screwy.
<br />

<br />
Personally I think the added dot focus is worth the effort.  However, if you already have Riz I can see how other needs might put Muse lower on the list of things to get from LDoN.</span></td>
